{"tid":1757567,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"689: 「請各區準備遍地開花」","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T17:48:08.000Z","uid":120847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e323f4ea6f11821f21588ea770378b3c6df5cbf9","tid":1757567,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/996399490722528/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100010574583275%2Fposts%2F996399490722528%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx96Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=4211189b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100010574583275/posts/996399490722528/</a><br />\n<br />\n給各建制派區議會候選人和廣大選民，<br />\n上山打游擊<br />\n1. 精神：悲憤過後，展示力量。<br />\n2. 優勢：大家在各區深耕多年，有紥實的人脈基礎，對地區問題有深入的認識。<br />\n3. 戰略：以其人之道，還治其人之身。大家調整姿態，做好在野黨和少數黨的角色，靈活多變，不排除任何合法手段。用地區議題和民生議題圍堵反對派的全港性政治議題。<br />\n4. 大環境：中央不會放水派糖，經濟衰退，各區氣氛在未來兩三個月會急轉直下。<br />\n5. 行動：馬上向當選的反對派議員（尤其是有機會成為區議會主席和副主席的）提工作要求。舉例：a. 聯同幾個街坊帶著油掃油漆要求這些人一起將區內的政治塗鴉塗上白漆，b.要求一起動手清理連儂牆， c.開列區內的老大難問題，請有意競逐主席副主席的人出席居民大會一一回應，用手機攝錄他們的反應然後上載。<br />\n6. 團結就是力量：<span style=\"color: red;\">舉行武林大會，建立各區各建制黨派連線，統籌協調行動，遍地開花。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 鼓勵街坊舉報當選議員的違法違規行為，包括僭建問題。<br />\n8. 財政：好商量。<br />\n<br />\n請廣大選民幫手。"},{"pid":"de7a7758e4eb1e0b70c29c5bfaa97af0c471a62b","tid":1757567,"uid":274538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DV4MUJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDV4MUJ3.jpg&h=b1f4ed06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff9192db07db79aed94017336315fb6f30f63e03","tid":1757567,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111a54e2da3843ae9d2df9b7dc85989796760a98","tid":1757567,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"財政：好商量。"},{"pid":"499f463b7e8dff5f02b896c715d64f2ec5346bc0","tid":1757567,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 傻閪"},{"pid":"102d5aedf9a93b74a0062c2b1bb69bd1065cb946","tid":1757567,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"老人院有冇安排旅遊巴出去區議會辦事處先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d444589a93fce91f71cecbe98dd27616e104f024","tid":1757567,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"武林大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會練練吓武死咗㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4aed2556644cd89e97c2e11255ec5d7bcfe519","tid":1757567,"uid":133279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"係咪中共肯開水喉用同等人工養住班落選人先<br />\n搞掂佢地餐晏仔先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77efcd64a577f0a6de29fcf2e8700f6d87ce1a99","tid":1757567,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"唔睇清楚以為陳雲出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b557d30ed7d90eb7e43a5415e19329e7450bacc4","tid":1757567,"uid":266051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:48:08.000Z"